title: Jason Ellis Is A Wild Man!! **Trigger Warning**
description:
You are going to LOVE this episode! Jason Ellis has done it all. At one point he was one of the biggest skaters in the world, massive radio DJ, Fighter, Comedian, and one of the funniest people I have ever met.  Also I recap my trip to Dubai!

**Trigger Warning** -- Jason goes into depth about abuse he suffered as a child, as well as other heavy topics.
